**Lemma 3.8**.: _Let \(u\) be the number of times that MaxCoverage\((k,r)\) updates heap \(H\). Then copying heap \(H_{r}\) in Line 2, as well as all these \(u\) updates, can be handled in total time \(O(u\log n)\)._

